<template>
  <b-row class="match-height">
    <b-col cols="12">
      <modal-basic />

    <b-col cols="12">
      <modal-theme />
    </b-col>
    <b-col cols="12">
      <modal-sizes />
    </b-col>
    <b-col cols="12">
      <modal-form-scroll />
    </b-col>
    <b-col md="6">
      <modal-variant />
    </b-col>
    <b-col md="6">

    <b-col cols="12">
      <modal-prevent />
    </b-col>
    <b-col cols="12">
      <modal-disbale-foooter />

import ModalFooterButtonSizing from './ModalFooterSizing.vue'

import ModalMessageBox from './ModalMessageBox.vue'
import ModalBasic from './ModalBasic.vue'
import ModalMethod from './ModalMethod.vue'

export default {
  components: {
    BCol,
    BRow,

    ModalFooterButtonSizing,
    ModalMultipleSupport,
    ModalPrevent,
    ModalSizes,
    ModalVariant,
    ModalVmodal,
    ModalTheme,
    ModalDisbaleFoooter,
    ModalMessageBox,
    ModalBasic,
    ModalMethod,
    ModalFormScroll,
  },
}
</script>
